<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to TransitLedger!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <%= fullName %>,</p>
    
    <p>Welcome to TransitLedger! We're excited to have you on board. Your account has been successfully verified and is ready to use.</p>
    
    <p>With TransitLedger, you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse available train schedules</li>
      <li>Book tickets for your journey</li>
      <li>Manage your bookings</li>
      <li>Verify your tickets</li>
      <li>And much more!</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Get started by logging into your account:</p>
    <a href="<%= process.env.CLIENT_URL %>/login" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TransitLedger. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 